snippet.title: Vigilance 2099 - Cyberpunk Teaser Gameplay ue4
snippet.description:
Vigilance 2099 is a cyberpunk bounty hunting game inspired by prey 2 and blade runner. What you are seeing is prototype gameplay with a lot more to come!
Website is now Live: https://www.vigilance2099.com/
For more info, check out our twitter page: https://twitter.com/NasNakarus
Feel free to join our discord! : https://discord.gg/CxUPhzC
